{"word":"Jephthah","slug":"jephthah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Jephthah</b> - son of Gilead, a deliverer of Israel, one of the judges<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=1'>Jdg 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=5'>Jdg 11:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=14'>Jdg 11:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=30'>Jdg 11:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=34'>Jdg 11:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=40'>Jdg 11:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=12&verse=2'>Jdg 12:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=12&verse=7'>Jdg 12:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=12&verse=11'>1Sa 12:11</a><p/>--Summary of his life<p/>An outcast<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=1'>Jdg 11:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=2'>Jdg 11:2</a><p/>Rises to leadership<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=4'>Jud 11:4-10</a><p/>Moved at times by God's Spirit<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=29'>Jud 11:29</a><p/>Made a rash vow<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=30'>Jdg 11:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=31'>Jdg 11:31</a><p/>Delivered Israel from their enemies<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=33'>Jud 11:33</a><p/>A man who kept his vow<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=11&verse=39'>Jud 11:39</a>"}]}